-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
SUMMARY (non-binding — see canonical text for the controlling terms)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The Space Child License is a source-available, peace-conditional software
license that grants broad permissions for peaceful use while creating
accountability when technology is directed toward harm.

Core principles:

  1. PEACE-POSITIVE
     The license actively encourages humanitarian use as the highest
     purpose of technology.

  2. DEFENSIVE USE PERMITTED
     Self-defense is recognized as a fundamental right. Defensive
     military use is permitted free of charge.

  3. WAR PAYS FOR PEACE
     Offensive military use requires a paid license. Twenty-five percent
     (25%) of revenue from such licenses is routed directly to peace
     organizations.

  4. COPYLEFT PEACE CLAUSE
     Derivative works inherit the peace conditions of this license.

  5. COMMERCIALLY VIABLE
     Peaceful commercial use is unrestricted.

  6. LEGALLY STRUCTURED
     The license is drafted to be enforceable, not merely aspirational.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
PERMITTED USES (non-exhaustive)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  - Personal, educational, and research use.
  - Peaceful commercial use, including SaaS and internal tooling.
  - Humanitarian, civil-defense, disaster-response, and public-safety use.
  - Defensive military use as defined in the canonical license text.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
USES REQUIRING A PAID OFFENSIVE-USE LICENSE
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  - Any offensive military application as defined in the canonical text.
  - Any use designed to identify, target, harm, surveil for harm, or
    deny basic human rights to civilians.

To obtain an offensive-use license (and trigger the 25% peace-revenue
disbursement), contact the licensor through the channels published at
https://legal.spacechild.love.

